lemma radical_sqrt_simultaneous_quadratic_quadratic: assumes a: "a \<in> radical_sqrt" and b: "b \<in> radical_sqrt" and c: "c \<in> radical_sqrt" and d: "d \<in> radical_sqrt" and e: "e \<in> radical_sqrt" and f: "f \<in> radical_sqrt" and NotEqual: "\<not> (a = d & b = e & c = f)" and eq0: "(x - a)^2 + (y - b)^2 = c" and eq1: "(x - d)^2 + (y - e)^2 = f" shows "x \<in> radical_sqrt & y \<in> radical_sqrt"
